content: So it has a viral thing piped into it with audio. There is a little dog barking at him and when he starts running, there is noise from a football game where the crowd goes "BLURRRR" when he catches it. There are captions at the bottom that follow a popular social media trend of football players asking the player they beat for the catch 'hey number 8, what's your favorite color' and then showing the clip where they got beat with the crowd going 'blurrrr'.
